{"tid":1740463,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【修例風波】網民發起觀塘「和你返」 學生一度走出馬路設路障","createTime":"2019-11-20T02:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T02:48:23.000Z","uid":56881,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"472c4ca09b46744d33dfb91817271500584c6390","tid":1740463,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:45:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98-%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0%E8%BF%94-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E5%BA%A6%E8%B5%B0%E5%87%BA%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF%E8%A8%AD%E8%B7%AF%E9%9A%9C-002500580.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598-%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E8%25BF%2594-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%259A%259C-002500580.html&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=9f4b7c67\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98-%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0%E8%BF%94-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E5%BA%A6%E8%B5%B0%E5%87%BA%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF%E8%A8%AD%E8%B7%AF%E9%9A%9C-002500580.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ne8pZsz8R5v3jgBD_vFlfQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191120a080216.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fne8pZsz8R5v3jgBD_vFlfQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191120a080216.jpg&h=ddaa21db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學生走出馬路。港台新聞截圖<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】本港全港小學、中學及部分特殊學校，今日恢復上課，有網民號召在觀塘發行「和你返」活動，一批身穿校服的學生響應，步行上學並走出馬通，現場交通受阻。防暴警員其後到場清理。<br />\n<br />\n今早7時許，一批身穿校服、戴有口罩的學生響應網上號召步行上學，當中部分人手持雨傘，他們走出協和街行車路，並高呼「五大訴求、缺一不可」等口號，現場交通受阻。<br />\n<br />\n期間有學生企圖以膠欄、鐵欄等雜物在多個路口設置路障，有司機不滿響號，更有人下車指罵學生，有學生向對方道歉，亦有市民將路障放回路邊，有人上前推撞學生，但被附近途人阻止。<br />\n<br />\n至8時許，一批防暴警察到場，現場學生其後散開。警員事後在場清理路障。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係要呢d"},{"pid":"475f95dc5834fdcb2e1847f0f68eb0e41df1d683","tid":1740463,"uid":8562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:45:46.000Z","msg":"呢代學生真係歷代至撚高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06739b755cb9f2cfd08c2d9c2389c5bdf859cba","tid":1740463,"uid":13774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}